ro-inverter, the transformer is the most difficult part to DIY. Because of =
the high frequency (100kHz), you cannot use a standard iron-core transforme=
r.</p><ul data-path-to-node=3D"12"><li><p data-path-to-node=3D"12,0,0"><b d=
ata-path-to-node=3D"12,0,0" data-index-in-node=3D"0">The Core:</b> You must=
