de=3D"12,1,0" data-index-in-node=3D"30">planar magnetics</b> or Litz wire t=
o minimize the "Skin Effect," where electricity only flows on the surface o=
f the wire at high frequencies, causing it to overheat.</p></li><li><p data=
-path-to-node=3D"12,2,0"><b data-path-to-node=3D"12,2,0" data-index-in-node=
=3D"0">Isolation:</b> The transformer provides the <b data-path-to-node=3D"=
12,2,0" data-index-in-node=3D"40">galvanic isolation</b> required by safety=
 standards, ensuring that 230V AC never travels back to your solar panels o=
r your DC battery.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=3D"13">4. Critical Sa=
fety Features for DIY</h3><p data-path-to-node=3D"14">TI's firmware for the=
